{
  "id": "adv_card_kkr_14_02",
  "title": "赤崎こころ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_office_night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "あー、笑った笑った\n{user}さんは悪戯し甲斐がありますねぇ",
      "startTime": 3.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "せめてもの情けに着替えを用意してくれていて\n助かったよ。あの姿を誰かに見られたらと思うと……",
      "startTime": 10.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "あははっ、またみんなに変態扱いされたり\nヤミちゃんに殴り飛ばされちゃうかもしれませんね",
      "startTime": 18.76739254,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "あれは本当に災難だった……\nこころも少しは加減してくれ",
      "startTime": 25.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、まだモモちゃんと一緒に練った悪戯が\nいーっぱいあるので、しばらくは楽しませて下さーい",
      "startTime": 31.8136968296,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……しばらくは覚悟しておくしかない、か\nしかし、こころはモモさん達と本当に相性がいいんだな",
      "startTime": 42.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "ふふふ、みなさん、こころには敵わないですけど\nとーっても可愛いですし、何より話が合いますから！",
      "startTime": 51.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "特にモモちゃんとは！　生き別れの姉妹だと\n思っちゃうほど仲良しになっちゃいまして～！",
      "startTime": 59.2683458012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "プリンとモモちゃんの大好きな紅茶を嗜みながら\nお茶会もとい悪戯会議をよくしているんですよ",
      "startTime": 65.8683468184,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "今は可愛い悪戯を愛ちゃんや古手川さんや\n莉央さんに仕掛ける作戦を一緒に考えてまして",
      "startTime": 73.6016801518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "お、恐ろしいお茶会を開くんじゃない……",
      "startTime": 77.4683468184,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、でも莉央さんが本当に強敵なんですよね～\nこの前なんて、計画をなぜか察知されて怒られちゃって",
      "startTime": 85.8471678259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "一週間、プリン禁止令を出されてしまいました\n莉央さんってば、本当に悪魔ですよね～",
      "startTime": 93.7805011592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（よっぽどこころとモモさんの方が悪魔に）\n（いや、小悪魔に見えるぞ、とは言わないでおこう）",
      "startTime": 101.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "し、しかし、俺以外には未遂で終わってるんだな\n莉央さんがちゃんと叱ってくれていて良かったよ",
      "startTime": 110.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "今は、ですけどね～\nなんとか一泡吹かせようとモモちゃんと話し合い中です",
      "startTime": 116.6341748399,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "しぶといな……\nこころらしいというか、なんというか",
      "startTime": 123.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "でもとっておきの悪戯を仕掛けたいのは\n莉央さんじゃないんですよねぇ",
      "startTime": 129.9529961429,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02-kkr012.m4a",
      "text": "まだ計画中なので、誰にとかは秘密ですが。それよりも\nクリスマスライブですよ！　準備は出来ていますか？",
      "startTime": 137.2196628096,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ。ライブ会場や告知の手配も済んでるし\n俺が出来ることは終えているよ",
      "startTime": 144.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02-kkr013.m4a",
      "text": "さすがですね～！　こころが褒めてあげます！\nあとはこころ達の練習次第、ですね",
      "startTime": 151.027577766,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02-kkr014.m4a",
      "text": "でも心配はいりませんよ！　こころ達がモモちゃん達に\n歌とダンスを教えていますからね！",
      "startTime": 158.7942515535,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02-kkr015.m4a",
      "text": "こころだってBIG4です！\n誇りにかけて、最高のライブにしますから！",
      "startTime": 163.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "俺は何も心配していないさ、楽しみにしているよ\nけど、まずは目の前の仕事だ",
      "startTime": 171.5092884544,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02-kkr016.m4a",
      "text": "ふふーん、今日の打ち合わせだってもうすでに\nみんながひっくり返るような案を考えてきましたから～",
      "startTime": 178.5781974001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "（頼もしい限りだ。これで悪戯さえしなければなぁ）\n（いや、それもこころの魅力の一つ、か）",
      "startTime": 188.3000010173,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――そしてクリスマスライブの後",
      "startTime": 193.0233087384,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 194.5566278303
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 194.7232995832
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様、凄かったぞ\n一夜限りにするのはもったいないライブだった！",
      "startTime": 198.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02-kkr017.m4a",
      "text": "当然です！　みんなで力を合わせたんですから！\nこころ達の魅力にお客さん達、メロメロでしたね～！",
      "startTime": 205.1821245357,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 209.3487871334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02-kkr018.m4a",
      "text": "この後、成功のお祝いに、寮で打ち上げをするんですが\n{user}さんもどうですか？",
      "startTime": 213.1821245357,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "嬉しい誘いだが、この後まだ仕事があってな\n終わったら顔を出すよ。お別れ会でもあるんだろ",
      "startTime": 219.5333343506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 223.6226875151
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02-kkr019.m4a",
      "text": "ライブのおかげで『ぴょんぴょんワープくん\nDXカスタム』のエネルギーも溜まったみたいですから",
      "startTime": 226.0560249174,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "ララさん達、帰れるみたいで良かったよ\nけど、寂しくなるな",
      "startTime": 233.9333343506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 236.521122917
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02-kkr020.m4a",
      "text": "夢みたいな素敵な毎日でしたねぇ\nずっとずっとモモちゃんと悪戯をしていたかったなぁ",
      "startTime": 240.1544481122,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_02-kkr021.m4a",
      "text": "でも悲しいだけのお別れなんて嫌ですから、打ち上げは\nこころのスマイルで最高の思い出にしてやります",
      "startTime": 249.021126986,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 252.721122917
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
